OL,5, Police in Thailand have arrested a     
OL,6, woman whose pet lion was pictured going
OL,7, on a joyride in the streets of Pattaya.
OL,9,FA video that has now gone viral shows  
OL,10,Fthe chained lion cub seated in the back
OL,11,Fof a white, open-top Bentley.          
OL,13,FThe lion was being driven about by a   
OL,14,FSri Lankan man who has since left the  
OL,15,Fcountry, and is believed to be a friend
OL,16,Fof Sawangjit Kosoongnern.              
OL,18,FWhile it is not illegal to own a lion  
OL,19,Fin Thailand, it needs to be officially 
OL,20,Fregistered.                            
